## Share an Analytics Dashboard View by Email
> This guide demonstrates how to share a read-only view of your analytics dashboard with colleagues via email.

1. From the analytics dashboard, click the **Share** icon in the top right corner of the **Test Coverage by Configuration** panel.
2. In the **Share 'Analytics & Trends' View** window, enter the recipient's name or email and select them from the list.

![Key Action Screenshot + current_step](data:image/png;base64,)

3. Set an **Expiration** date and add a personal note in the **Message (Optional)** field.
4. Click the **Share** button to send the email invitation.

![Key Action Screenshot + current_step](data:image/png;base64,)

5. From the received email, click the **Open dashboard** button to access the shared view.

![Key Action Screenshot + current_step](data:image/png;base64,)


###  Result
The recipient can now access a read-only view of the shared analytics dashboard.

![Result Screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)
